	========================================================================== */

/*
[OVERVIEW] Polyfill for the native loading="lazy" attribute:
https://github.com/mfranzke/loading-attribute-polyfill

[INFO] Content of “loading-attribute-polyfill.css”:
https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/loading-attribute-polyfill/dist/loading-attribute-polyfill.min.css
 */
